# Build and release packaging

- Keep aligned when changing bundled runtime locations: `build/prepare-resources.js`, `build/download-manifest.js`, `package.json` `extraResources`, `src/main.js` path resolution.
- `build/resources/resource-manifest.json` must invalidate stale prepared resources when inputs change.
- Windows packaged Python: `python311._pth` includes `../backend`; dev mode uses `PYTHONPATH` in `src/main.js`.
- macOS helper: build from `swift/AudioCaptureHelper`, copy via `prepare-resources.js`, sign in `electron-builder` as `Contents/Resources/bin/audiocapture-helper`.
- Installer filename patterns: if release artifact names change, update `src/updater.js` and `.github/workflows/build-release.yml`.
